Actions.Text: AMEND AND RECOMMIT TO LOCAL GOVERNMENTS

Title: Authorizes the town of Ithaca, county of Tompkins to discontinue as parklands and alienate certain lands
Summary: Authorizes the town of Ithaca, county of Tompkins, to discontinue as parklands and alienate certain lands for the purpose of maintaining and operating such lands for agricultural purposes.
ActClause: AN ACT in relation to authorizing the town of Ithaca to alienate and discontinue the use of certain parklands
